{
  "id": null,
  "uid": "latency-overview",
  "title": "Latência de Requisições - Conversational AI",
  "tags": ["conversational-ai", "latency"],
  "timezone": "browser",
  "schemaVersion": 39,
  "version": 1,
  "refresh": "10s",
  "time": { "from": "now-1h", "to": "now" },
  "panels": [
    {
      "id": 100,
      "type": "row",
      "title": "Média de tempo de requisição por serviço",
      "gridPos": { "h": 1, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 0 },
      "collapsed": false,
      "panels": []
    },
    {
      "id": 1,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Latência média por serviço (ms)",
      "description": "Média = taxa da soma das durações / taxa da contagem de requisições, por instância de serviço. Cobre os 9 serviços de aplicação (platform_http_request_duration_seconds).",
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
      "gridPos": { "h": 9, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 1 },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "ms",
          "custom": { "drawStyle": "line", "lineWidth": 2, "fillOpacity": 10, "spanNulls": true }
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": {
        "legend": { "displayMode": "table", "placement": "right", "calcs": ["mean", "max", "last"] },
        "tooltip": { "mode": "multi" }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
          "expr": "1000 * sum by (instance) (rate(platform_http_request_duration_seconds_sum{job=~\"dotnet-services|python-services\"}[$__rate_interval])) / sum by (instance) (rate(platform_http_request_duration_seconds_count{job=~\"dotnet-services|python-services\"}[$__rate_interval]))",
          "legendFormat": "{{instance}}"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "type": "table",
      "title": "Latência média por serviço + endpoint (ms) - janela selecionada",
      "description": "Detalhe por método/path dentro de cada serviço. Ordene pela coluna Value para achar o endpoint mais lento.",
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
      "gridPos": { "h": 10, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 10 },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": { "unit": "ms", "custom": { "align": "auto" } },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": {
        "showHeader": true,
        "sortBy": [{ "displayName": "Value", "desc": true }]
      },
      "transformations": [
        { "id": "merge", "options": {} },
        { "id": "organize", "options": { "excludeByName": { "Time": true } } }
      ],
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
          "instant": true,
          "format": "table",
          "expr": "1000 * sum by (instance, method, path) (increase(platform_http_request_duration_seconds_sum{job=~\"dotnet-services|python-services\"}[$__range])) / (sum by (instance, method, path) (increase(platform_http_request_duration_seconds_count{job=~\"dotnet-services|python-services\"}[$__range])) > 0)"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 101,
      "type": "row",
      "title": "E2E aproximado: webhook recebido no BFF → resposta enviada à Meta",
      "gridPos": { "h": 1, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 20 },
      "collapsed": false,
      "panels": []
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "type": "text",
      "title": "",
      "gridPos": { "h": 3, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 21 },
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "**Aproximação, não um relógio único de ponta a ponta.** O envio da resposta ao cliente acontece de forma assíncrona via outbox do orchestrator, sem instrumentação própria de E2E. **A etapa 2 (Orchestrator) já inclui a etapa 3 (Agent Runtime) dentro de si** — `IngestMessageUseCase` mede o tempo total do turno, incluindo a chamada ao Agent Runtime, então a etapa 3 é mostrada só para referência/diagnóstico e **não entra na soma do Total**. Total = etapa 1 + etapa 2 (que já contém a 3) + etapa 4. Não incluído no total: tempo de fila no Kafka, espera no outbox antes do dispatch."
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "1. Webhook recebido (BFF)",
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
      "gridPos": { "h": 5, "w": 4, "x": 0, "y": 24 },
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "unit": "ms", "decimals": 1 }, "overrides": [] },
      "options": { "reduceOptions": { "calcs": ["lastNotNull"] }, "graphMode": "area" },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
          "expr": "1000 * sum(rate(platform_http_request_duration_seconds_sum{instance=\"whatsapp-bff:8080\",method=\"POST\",path=\"/webhooks/whatsapp\"}[$__rate_interval])) / sum(rate(platform_http_request_duration_seconds_count{instance=\"whatsapp-bff:8080\",method=\"POST\",path=\"/webhooks/whatsapp\"}[$__rate_interval]))"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 5,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "2. Processamento (Orchestrator, já inclui a etapa 3)",
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
      "gridPos": { "h": 5, "w": 4, "x": 4, "y": 24 },
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "unit": "ms", "decimals": 1 }, "overrides": [] },
      "options": { "reduceOptions": { "calcs": ["lastNotNull"] }, "graphMode": "area" },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
          "expr": "1000 * sum(rate(orchestrator_message_processing_duration_seconds_sum[$__rate_interval])) / sum(rate(orchestrator_message_processing_duration_seconds_count[$__rate_interval]))"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 6,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "3. Chamada ao Agent Runtime (subconjunto da etapa 2, não somado no Total)",
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
      "gridPos": { "h": 5, "w": 4, "x": 8, "y": 24 },
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "unit": "ms", "decimals": 1 }, "overrides": [] },
      "options": { "reduceOptions": { "calcs": ["lastNotNull"] }, "graphMode": "area" },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
          "expr": "1000 * sum(rate(orchestrator_agent_runtime_call_duration_seconds_sum[$__rate_interval])) / sum(rate(orchestrator_agent_runtime_call_duration_seconds_count[$__rate_interval]))"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 7,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "4. Envio à Meta (BFF)",
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
      "gridPos": { "h": 5, "w": 4, "x": 12, "y": 24 },
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "unit": "ms", "decimals": 1 }, "overrides": [] },
      "options": { "reduceOptions": { "calcs": ["lastNotNull"] }, "graphMode": "area" },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
          "expr": "1000 * sum(rate(platform_http_request_duration_seconds_sum{instance=\"whatsapp-bff:8080\",method=\"POST\",path=\"/internal/messages\"}[$__rate_interval])) / sum(rate(platform_http_request_duration_seconds_count{instance=\"whatsapp-bff:8080\",method=\"POST\",path=\"/internal/messages\"}[$__rate_interval]))"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 8,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Total aproximado (etapas 1 + 2 + 4, sem dupla contagem)",
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
      "gridPos": { "h": 5, "w": 8, "x": 16, "y": 24 },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "ms",
          "decimals": 1,
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              { "color": "green", "value": null },
              { "color": "yellow", "value": 3000 },
              { "color": "red", "value": 8000 }
            ]
          }
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": { "reduceOptions": { "calcs": ["lastNotNull"] }, "graphMode": "area" },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
          "expr": "1000 * ( (sum(rate(platform_http_request_duration_seconds_sum{instance=\"whatsapp-bff:8080\",method=\"POST\",path=\"/webhooks/whatsapp\"}[$__rate_interval])) / sum(rate(platform_http_request_duration_seconds_count{instance=\"whatsapp-bff:8080\",method=\"POST\",path=\"/webhooks/whatsapp\"}[$__rate_interval]))) + (sum(rate(orchestrator_message_processing_duration_seconds_sum[$__rate_interval])) / sum(rate(orchestrator_message_processing_duration_seconds_count[$__rate_interval]))) + (sum(rate(platform_http_request_duration_seconds_sum{instance=\"whatsapp-bff:8080\",method=\"POST\",path=\"/internal/messages\"}[$__rate_interval])) / sum(rate(platform_http_request_duration_seconds_count{instance=\"whatsapp-bff:8080\",method=\"POST\",path=\"/internal/messages\"}[$__rate_interval]))) )"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 9,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Breakdown ao longo do tempo (ms) - etapas 1+2+4 empilhadas, etapa 3 sobreposta como referência",
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
      "gridPos": { "h": 9, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 29 },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "ms",
          "custom": {
            "drawStyle": "line",
            "lineWidth": 1,
            "fillOpacity": 30,
            "stacking": { "mode": "normal", "group": "A" },
            "spanNulls": true
          }
        },
        "overrides": [
          {
            "matcher": { "id": "byName", "options": "3. Chamada ao Agent Runtime (referência, dentro da etapa 2)" },
            "properties": [
              { "id": "custom.stacking", "value": { "mode": "none", "group": "A" } },
              { "id": "custom.lineStyle", "value": { "dash": [10, 10], "fill": "dash" } },
              { "id": "custom.fillOpacity", "value": 0 },
              { "id": "custom.lineWidth", "value": 2 }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      "options": {
        "legend": { "displayMode": "table", "placement": "bottom", "calcs": ["mean", "max"] },
        "tooltip": { "mode": "multi" }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
          "expr": "1000 * sum(rate(platform_http_request_duration_seconds_sum{instance=\"whatsapp-bff:8080\",method=\"POST\",path=\"/webhooks/whatsapp\"}[$__rate_interval])) / sum(rate(platform_http_request_duration_seconds_count{instance=\"whatsapp-bff:8080\",method=\"POST\",path=\"/webhooks/whatsapp\"}[$__rate_interval]))",
          "legendFormat": "1. Webhook recebido (BFF)"
        },
        {
          "refId": "B",
          "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
          "expr": "1000 * sum(rate(orchestrator_message_processing_duration_seconds_sum[$__rate_interval])) / sum(rate(orchestrator_message_processing_duration_seconds_count[$__rate_interval]))",
          "legendFormat": "2. Processamento (Orchestrator, inclui etapa 3)"
        },
        {
          "refId": "C",
          "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
          "expr": "1000 * sum(rate(orchestrator_agent_runtime_call_duration_seconds_sum[$__rate_interval])) / sum(rate(orchestrator_agent_runtime_call_duration_seconds_count[$__rate_interval]))",
          "legendFormat": "3. Chamada ao Agent Runtime (referência, dentro da etapa 2)"
        },
        {
          "refId": "D",
          "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
          "expr": "1000 * sum(rate(platform_http_request_duration_seconds_sum{instance=\"whatsapp-bff:8080\",method=\"POST\",path=\"/internal/messages\"}[$__rate_interval])) / sum(rate(platform_http_request_duration_seconds_count{instance=\"whatsapp-bff:8080\",method=\"POST\",path=\"/internal/messages\"}[$__rate_interval]))",
          "legendFormat": "4. Envio à Meta (BFF)"
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
